snippet.title: Awakened: Dark Space Alpha Trailer#1
snippet.description:
First Trailer showing the overall atmosphere.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1469490/Awakened_Dark_Space/
https://twitter.com/moonloregames

Awakened: Dark Space is an atmospheric horror game with a unique mix of medieval, present and sci-fi elements.

About 900 years ago in the Crystal Woods Castle everyone died and until today there are endless rumors about missing people in this area. Some think of it as a challenge to go into the woods or research but everyone who goes in too far is never seen again. The only thing that is left of them, is their voices...
